Above is a 6th Grade Cursive Handwriting Practice Sheet with the above Quote. The Cryptos are Falling Asleep! Bitcoin has died again. It did it so quietly no one even noticed it passed. It could not inspire faith in anyone anymore. It was the faith which held it alive and now we know how fragile benchmarks can get when they are imaginary.

Craig Wright is back and he is waving around his blue prints to prove to his ex-colleagues that his creation Bitcoin Satoshi Vision is the real one. In his minds Bitcoin has never died. Wright is so sure he’ll be able to convince the world of his Litecoin that he has a brilliant idea of finally going to jail for his previous concoction.
